  "texts": [
    "L2 features are stored in BigTable.",
    "Every L2 ID matches to a row in BigTable and contains a column for each feature.",
    "Edits require the calculation of new meshes and L2 features for all newly generated L2 IDs.",
    "This is an expandable set of work tasks that we keep independent from the ChunkedGraph service to increase modularity and expandability.",
    "After every edit, the ChunkedGraph adds a message to a queuing system (Extended Data Fig. 3) to which individual services can subscribe."
